        <p>We ran 10 platforms across 17 real locations for 90 days. Here is the ranking by what each piece of software actually delivers — not feature lists, but live outputs.</p>

        <div class="callout callout-tldr">
          <div class="callout-label">TL;DR — Pick by what you actually want</div>
