        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Want the outcome, not the dashboard?</h4>
            <p>theStacc ships local landing pages, GBP posts, and citations as a managed service. <strong>$49/mo Local SEO, $167/mo full bundle</strong> — one bill, no logins to babysit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">See a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · 15-min walkthrough</span>
          </div>
