          <div class="callout-label">The "dashboard tax" trap</div>
          <p>Operators routinely pay $200+/mo for three dashboards that each show a slice of the problem — <strong>and still have no published local page or scheduled GBP post to show for it.</strong> Buy software only if you have the operator hours to act on what it shows.</p>
